reviewText: It is a walk down the avenue of memories and Entreteniemiento of children recommended for those who like the cartoon fantasies.
The English version cost more, the Spanish version is cheaper and also comes with the English audio.

Wow! what a nice surprise! I being looking for this TV series for years and I finally find it, this is one of my favorite cartoons of all times. You do not know how much I being missing you Princesa Amanecer! Just love it.

During the childhood of many Mexicans that now we are in the 30 `s or more this cartoon plenty our days of TV, along with Top Cat, The Flinstones, Wicky Races and Scooby Doo (Don Gato, Los Picapiedra y Carrera de Locos in spanish) all became classic of those times. It`s brilliant that now we can to enjoy again.

I am very happy with this purchasing, the quality are really good, and the cartoons are exactly as I remember on my childhood,

I really enjoy it.
